# SpendTracker

SpendTracker is an application for tracking your expenses and visualizing them with graphs. With SpendTracker, you can easily keep track of your expenses and understand how you are spending your money.

## Features

- Add expenses and custom categories.
- Visualize expenses with clear and easy-to-understand graphs.
- Analyze expenses by category and period.
- Receive expense notifications to stay on track.
- Set spending limits for each category to avoid overspending.

## How to Use

1. Download and install the SpendTracker application on your device.
2. Create a user account and log in to the application.
3. Add your expenses by selecting a category and entering the amount spent.
4. Check the graphs to visualize your expenses by category and period.
5. Use the spending limits for each category to avoid overspending.

SpendTracker is an easy-to-use and convenient application for anyone who wants to track their expenses and visualize their spending habits. If you have any questions or comments, please contact us at support@spendtracker.com.